msgid "Necessary"
msgstr "必要"

#: src/Admin/ModulesPage.php:1106
msgid ""
"Used only when deferring fonts until consent. Requires the Consent Manager "
"module to be enabled."
msgstr "仅在将字体延迟到同意之后时使用。需要启用同意管理器模块。"

#: src/Admin/ModulesPage.php:1112
msgid "Custom Integrations"
msgstr "自定义集成"

#: src/Admin/ModulesPage.php:1113
msgid ""
"Add your own scripts or snippets to the page head or footer. Each snippet is "
"assigned a consent category and runs only after the visitor grants it, via "
"the Consent Manager."
msgstr ""
"将您自己的脚本或代码片段添加到页面的 head 或 footer 中。每个代码片段都会被分"
"配一个同意类别，并通过同意管理器仅在访客授予后才运行。"

#: src/Admin/ModulesPage.php:1114 src/Admin/ModulesPage.php:1128
#: src/Admin/ModulesPage.php:2301
msgid "Advanced & Tools"
msgstr "高级与工具"

#: src/Admin/ModulesPage.php:1119
msgid ""
"Each snippet is emitted as a consent-gated placeholder and only executes "
"once the matching category is granted. Necessary snippets always run. "
"Requires the Consent Manager module to actually gate execution."
msgstr ""
"每个代码片段都会作为受同意控制的占位符输出，仅在相应类别获得授予后才执行。必"
"要的代码片段始终运行。需要同意管理器模块才能真正控制执行。"

#: src/Admin/ModulesPage.php:1120
msgid "Snippets"
msgstr "代码片段"

#: src/Admin/ModulesPage.php:1126
msgid "Custom Triggers"
msgstr "自定义触发器"

#: src/Admin/ModulesPage.php:1127
msgid ""
"Push your own dataLayer events on simple page conditions, such as visiting a "
"URL or clicking an element. Integrates with the GA4 DataLayer module."
msgstr ""
"在简单的页面条件下（例如访问某个 URL 或点击某个元素）推送您自己的 dataLayer "
"事件。与 GA4 DataLayer 模块集成。"

#: src/Admin/ModulesPage.php:1133
msgid ""
"Each trigger pushes an event into window.dataLayer. Assign a consent "
"category to hold a trigger until that category is granted (necessary always "
"fires)."
msgstr ""
"每个触发器都会向 window.dataLayer 推送一个事件。为触发器分配一个同意类别，可"
"将其保留到该类别获得授予后再触发（必要类别始终触发）。"

